Chancey Allen Luna was found guilty of first-degree murder in the August 2013 shooting death of Christopher Lane . 
  Lane was shot in the back while out for a jog in Duncan, Oklahoma . 
  The jury recommended that Luna be sentenced to life in prison without parole . 
  Luna told reporters he was 'sorry' as he was led out of the courtroom . 
  His mother testified that her son meant only to scare Lane . 
 